<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Giant" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Giant,</orth> a person of extraordinary size and power: <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.108" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 2, 108</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.108" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 2, 108</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.81" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 81</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.205" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 1, 205</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.218" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 218</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 1.225" default="NO" valid="yes">John I, 225</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.2.57" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.5.45" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.345" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 345</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.147" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 147</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 2, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.91" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 3, 5</bibl>. Adjectively, == enormous, monstrous: <cit><quote>a g. traitor,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.199" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 2, 199</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>